%20after%20hitting%20the%20first%20vehicle%2C%20the%20police%20have%20told%20a%20court%20in%20the%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh%20Ordered%20400%20Bolero%20SUVs%20For%20SOS%20Calls.%20They%20Are%20Rotting%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20instance%20of%20the%20wastage%20of%20taxpayers'%20money%2C%20four%20hundred%20Mahindra%20Bolero%20SUVs%20are%20rotting%20unused%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20third%20battalion%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20Security%20Force%20in%20the%20state's%20Durg%20district.%C2%A0The%20vehicles%20were%20bought%20last%20year%20for%20the%20state's%20emergency%20Dial-112%20service%20across%2022%20cities.%20They%20were%20to%20respond%20to%20SOS%20calls%2C%20including%20taking%20people%20to%20hospitals%20and%20aiding%20disaster%20response.%20Then%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel-led%20Congress%20government%20was%20voted%20out%2C%20and%20for%20over%20a%20year%20now%2C%20these%20SUVs%20are%20rotting%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20these%20vehicles%20procured%20for%20emergency%20services%20are%20lying%20unused%2C%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20are%20witnessing%20instances%20of%20big%20gaps%20in%20disaster%20response%20and%20the%20unavailability%20of%20public%20vehicles%20during%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manendragarh-Chirmiri-Bharatpur%20district%2C%20represented%20in%20the%20Assembly%20by%20Health%20Minister%20Shyam%20Bihari%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20woman%20fractured%20her%20leg%20and%20called%20an%20ambulance.%20The%20ambulance%20never%20arrived%2C%20and%20the%20family%20had%20to%20transport%20the%20woman%20to%20the%20hospital%20on%20a%20cot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20called%20the%20ambulance%2C%20but%20they%20told%20us%20it%20was%20picking%20up%20another%20patient.%20We%20were%20asked%20to%20take%20the%20patient%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Parmeshwar%2C%20the%20woman's%20relative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20such%20case%20in%20Ambikapur%2C%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20called%20an%20ambulance%20after%20she%20went%20into%20labour.%20The%20ambulance%20did%20not%20come%20and%20the%20family%20had%20to%20take%20her%20to%20hospital%20on%20a%20cot.%20Dr.%20Shailendra%20Gupta%20of%20Ambikapur%20district%20hospital%20said%20the%20ambulance%20had%20reached%20the%20main%20road%2C%20but%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20woman's%20doorstep.%20%26quot%3BThis%20highlights%20the%20road%20access%20issue%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20Surguja%2C%20where%20large%20vehicles%20can%20only%20reach%20the%20main%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20inadequate%20resources%20and%20major%20gaps%20in%20disaster%20response%20leading%20to%20such%20instances%20every%20other%20day%2C%20the%20sight%20of%20400%20SUVs%20that%20are%20lying%20unused%20despite%20being%20procured%20for%20these%20situations%20raises%20big%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicles%20were%20purchased%20for%20Rs%2040%20crore%20in%20July-August%20last%20year%2C%20months%20before%20the%20BJP%20government%20came%20to%20power.%20They%20have%20remained%20parked%20since%20then.%C2%A0Vijay%20Sharma%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20raised%20questions%20regarding%20the%20status%20of%20these%20vehicles%20and%20why%20they%20remain%20unused.%20We%20will%20soon%20receive%20an%20answer.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Those%20in%20the%20know%20say%20it%20will%20take%20at%20least%205-6%20months%20for%20a%20new%20tender%20to%20be%20issued%20so%20that%20the%20vehicles%20can%20be%20put%20to%20use.%20Once%20that%20happens%2C%20each%20SUV%20will%20require%20maintenance%20costing%20at%20least%20Rs%2020%2C000%20before%20they%20can%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733839620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Flq02j71_anurag-bolero_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-ne