chip%2C%20called%20Willow%2C%20can%20perform%20a%20standard%20benchmark%20computation%20in%20under%20five%20minutes.%20The%20same%20task%20would%20take%20the%20current%20fastest%20supercomputers%2010%20septillion%20years%2C%20longer%20than%20the%20universe%20had%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsundarpichai%2Fstatus%2F1866167429367468422%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Egoogle%257Ctwcamp%255Eserp%257Ctwgr%255Etweet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20post%20on%20December%209%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%20the%20chip%20cracked%20%26quot%3Ba%2030-year%20challenge%20in%20the%20field.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20Willow%20as%20an%20important%20step%20in%20our%20journey%20to%20build%20a%20useful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-investment-is-unlocking-innovation-in-the-quantum-and-space-sectors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20computer%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20practical%20applications%20in%20areas%20like%20drug%20discovery%2C%20fusion%20energy%2C%20battery%20design%20%2B%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20follow-up%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20chip%20won%20praise%20from%20other%20leading%20tech%20figures%2C%20including%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Sam%20Altman.%20Altman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20reposted%20the%20announcement%20congratulating%20the%20company%20on%20the%20development%2C%20while%20Musk%20replied%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1866170803051499874%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPachai's%20post%20saying%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BWow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20development%20represents%20a%20key%20milestone%20in%20the%20decadeslong%20race%20to%20build%20quantum%20computers%20that%20are%20accurate%20enough%20to%20have%20practical%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuantum%20computers%20use%20quantum%20mechanics%20to%20solve%20problems%20faster%20than%20traditional%20computing.%20Qubits%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20unit%20of%20information%20in%20quantum%20computing%20%E2%80%94%20are%20unpredictable%20and%20have%20high%20error%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20more%20qubits%20a%20chip%20has%20the%20more%20errors%20appear.%20This%20has%20been%20an%20outstanding%20challenge%20in%20the%20field%20since%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20show%20progress%2C%20quantum%20computers%20must%20demonstrate%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bbelow%20threshold%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20they%20can%20drive%20errors%20down%20while%20scaling%20up%20the%20number%20of%20qubits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20published%20an%20experiment%20in%20the%20science%20journal%20Nature%20on%20Monday%20showing%20the%20new%20potential%20of%20the%20Willow%20chip.%20The%20study%20demonstrated%20that%20the%20more%20qubits%20are%20scaled%20up%20in%20the%20Willow%20chip%2C%20the%20lower%20the%20rate%20of%20error.%20Google%20also%20said%20errors%20in%20their%20new%20chip%20can%20be%20corrected%20as%20they%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20of%20Google's%20Quantum%20AI%20lab%2C%20Michael%20Cuthbert%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc791ng0zvl3o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20commercial%20applications%20for%20a%20quantum%20computing%20chip%20would%20still%20not%20be%20available%20before%202030%2C%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20praised%20the%20company's%20efforts%20as%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20work%20shows%20a%20truly%20remarkable%20technological%20breakthrough%2C%26quot%3B%20Chao-Yang%20Lu%2C%20a%20quantum%20physicist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20of%20China%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0ad31943d0810888daf73eddf85cce15946d5731566c9d6d5a5be79f0eddab46%26postID%3D675833dfb9424548535106e4%26postSlug%3Dgoogle-unveiled-