oss-maha-aghadi-to-launch-anti-evm-protest-7116231%5C%22%3E%20planning%20a%20national%20protest%20against%20the%20credibility%20of%20EVMs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20blames%20for%20its%20dismal%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20protested%20against%20the%20use%20of%20voting%20machines%20and%20suggested%20a%20return%20to%20ballot%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20all%20unite%20and%20move%20forward%20together%20and%20push%20them%20aside.%20I%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20speak%20about%20elections%2C%20but%20I%20would%20surely%20say%20the%20votes%20of%20all%20the%20poor%20and%20oppressed%20communities%20are%20going%20to%20waste.%20They%20should%20all%20demand%20voting%20by%20ballot%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2082-year-old%20Congress%20chief%20said%20speaking%20at%20the%20'Samvidhan%20Rakshak%20Abhiyaan'%20function%20at%20Talkatora%20stadium%20in%20Delhi%20On%20November%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20keep%20EVMs%20with%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-want-evms-we-want-ballot-paper-mallikarjun-kharge-days-after-maharashtra-loss-7110356%5C%22%3EWe%20don't%20want%20EVMs%2C%20we%20want%20voting%20on%20ballot%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%20they%20will%20know%20what%20their%20position%20is%20and%20where%20they%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20over%20their%20allegation%20surrounding%20EVMs%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20on%20Sunday%20said%20let%20MLAs%20resign%20and%20let%20re-election%20take%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20takes%20them%20(MVA)%20seriously...If%20they%20don't%20have%20trust%20in%20EVMs%20the%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20of%20Congress%2C%20NCP-SCP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20should%20resign%20in%20protest%20of%20EVMs%20and%20let%20re-election%20take%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733836020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Frd07ebj8_karnataka-evm-generic_625x300_12_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-evm-vvpat-mismatch-election-body-amid-oppositions-maharashtra-claims-7216233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20is%20no%20mismatch%20between%20VVPAT%20slips%20(Voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail)%20and%20voting%20machine%20(EVM)%20numbers%2C%20said%20Chief%20Election%20Officer%20Maharashtra%2C%20rejecting%20the%20Opposition%20allegations%20about%20a%20vote%20mismatch%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-evm-vvpat-mismatch-election-body-amid-oppositions-maharashtra-claims-7216233%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNDA%20Has%20Majority%26quot%3B%3A%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20On%20No-Trust%20Motion%20Against%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20gave%20a%20reality%20check%20to%20the%20Opposition%20today%20on%20their%20no-trust%20motion%20against%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20which%20was%20filed%20with%20signatures%20of%2050-plus%20MPs.%20The%20Opposition%20--%20which%20shared%20a%20stormy%20relation%20with%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20--%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20partisanship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NDA%20has%20majority%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha...%20The%20notice%20must%20be%20rejected%2C%20will%20be%20rejected%20and%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20action%20is%20not%20accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20is%20our%20guide...%20One%20has%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20chair%20for%20proper%20conduction%20of%20the%20business%20of%20the%20House.%20The%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies