0a%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%2C%20originally%20from%20Bihar%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Manjunath%20Layout%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Neighbours%20found%20him%20hanging%20after%20breaking%20into%20the%20flat.%20A%20placard%20that%20read%2C%20%26quot%3Bjustice%20is%20due%26quot%3B%20was%20found%20in%20his%20room.%20His%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar%20told%20police%20that%20Atul's%20estranged%20wife%20had%20filed%20false%20cases%20against%20him%20and%20his%20parents%20and%20that%20he%20was%20mentally%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20has%20made%20serious%20allegations%20against%20his%20wife%2C%20her%20family%20members%20and%20a%20judge%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jaunpur%20in%20a%20video.%20He%20has%20also%20left%20behind%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20President%2C%20in%20which%20he%20criticised%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20and%20flagged%20a%20trend%20of%20false%20cases.%20In%20another%20note%2C%20he%20has%20said%20he%20pleads%20not%20guilty%20to%20all%20the%20charges%20brought%20against%20him%20by%20his%20wife.%20These%20include%20charges%20under%20the%20Dowry%20Prohibition%20Act%20and%20relevant%20sections%20such%20as%20causing%20hurt%20or%20cruelty%20against%20a%20woman%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20%26quot%3BI%20humbly%20request%20the%20court%20to%20stop%20harassing%20my%20parents%20and%20brother%20in%20these%20false%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20he%20recorded%20before%20dying%20by%20suicide%20and%20in%20the%20note%20he%20left%20behind%2C%20Atul%20Subhash%20said%20he%20married%20in%202019%20after%20a%20match%20on%20a%20matrimonial%20website.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20the%20next%20year.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife's%20family%20would%20repeatedly%20demand%20money%20running%20into%20several%20lakhs.%20When%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20more%20money%2C%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20home%20with%20their%20son%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%