0Justice%20Shekhar%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%C2%A0National%20Conference%20National%20Conference%20MP%20Aga%20Syed%20Ruhullah%20has%20said%20he%20would%20move%20a%20motion%20in%20Parliament%20for%20his%20impeachment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20provincial%20convention%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad's%20law%20cell%20(Kashi%20Province)%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Justice%20Yadav%20purportedly%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bcountry%20would%20function%20as%20per%20the%20wishes%20of%20the%20'bahusankhyak'%20(majority)%20living%20in%20Hindustan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20stating%20that%20this%20is%20Hindustan%2C%20and%20this%20country%20will%20function%20according%20to%20the%20wishes%20of%20the%20majority%20living%20here.%20This%20is%20the%20law.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20speaking%20as%20a%20High%20Court%20Judge%3B%20rather%2C%20the%20law%20operates%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20bahusankyak%20(majority).%20Consider%20this%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20family%20or%20society%20-%20only%20what%20ensures%20the%20welfare%20and%20happiness%20of%20the%20majority%20will%20be%20accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Yadav%20had%20purportedly%20said.%20Apparently%20he%20also%20used%20pejorative%20terms%20for%20Muslims%20and%20said%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdetrimental%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20judge%20who%20makes%20such%20a%20statement%20is%20violating%20his%20oath%20of%20office.%20If%20he%20is%20violating%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20he%20has%20no%20right%20to%20sit%20on%20that%20chair%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20convenor%20of%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%20(CJAR)%2C%20urged%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20to%20begin%20an%20in-house%20inquiry%20against%20Justice%20Yadav%20for%20%26quot%3Bjudicial%20impropriety%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bviolating%20the%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20judges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20newspaper%20reports%20of%20a%20speech%20given%20by%20Mr%20Justice%20Shekhar%20Kumar%20Yadav%2C%20a%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Judicature%20at%20Allahabad.%20The%20details%20and%20particulars%20have%20been%20called%20from%20the%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20under%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733834700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmpbrq8a_allahabad-high-court_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-allahabad-high-court-judges-india-will-run-by-wishes-of-majority-comment-7216256%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20remarks%20of%20a%20High%20Court%20judge%20about%20theb%20majority%20community's%20rule%20prevailing%20in%20a%20country%20have%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%2C%20with%20many%20demanding%20action%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-allahabad-high-court-judges-india-will-run-by-wishes-of-majority-comment-7216256%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Brian%20Thompson%20killer%20suspect%20Luigi%20Mangione%20in%20a%20relationship%3F%20Wild%20conspiracy%20theories%20claim...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733834684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116175919%2Cimgsize-931412.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-brian-thompson-killer-suspect-luigi-mangione-in-a-relationship-wild-conspiracy-theories-claim-%2Farticleshow%2F116175878.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116175878.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELuigi%20Mangione%2C%20the%20person%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20was%20reportedly%20not%20dating%20anyone%20or%20in%20a%20relationship%20because%20of%20his%20spine%20condition.%20%26quot%3BHe%20knew%20that%20dating%20and%20being%20physically%20intimate%20with%20his%20back%20condition%20wasn't%20possible.%20I%20remember%20him%20telling%20me%20that%2C%20and%20my%20heart%20just%20breaks%2C%26quot%3B%20RJ%20Martin%2C%20close%20to%20Mangione%2C%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-brian-thompson-killer-suspect-luigi-mangione-in-a-relationship-wild-conspiracy-theories-claim-%2Farticleshow%2F116175878.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-brian-thompson-killer-suspect-luigi-mangione-in-a-relationship-wild-conspiracy-theories-claim-%2Famp_articleshow%2F116175878.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-brian-thompson-killer-suspect-luigi-mangione-in-a-relationship-wild-conspiracy-theories-claim-%2Famp_articleshow%2F116175878.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20Change%20In%20India%20XI%20For%203rd%20Aus%20Test%3F%20Pujara%20Says%20%26quot%3BBatting%20Wasn't%20Good...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20crushing%20ten-wicket%20defeat%20to%20Australia%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20India's%20hopes%20of%20bouncing%20back%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20in%20Brisbane%20have%20taken%20centre%20stage.%20With%20the%20series%20tied%201-1%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20higher%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20seasoned%20batter%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20has%20suggested%20a%20key%20change%20to%20the%20playing%20XI.%20Pujara%20advocated%20for%20Washington%20Sundar's%20inclusion%20in%20place%20of%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20to%20bolster%20India's%20batting%20depth%20and%20regain%20control%20in%20the%20crucial%20series.%20Pujara's%20recommendation%20comes%20after%20Ashwin's%20underwhelming%20performance%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20where%20he%20managed%20figures%20of%201%2F53%20in%2018%20overs.%20While%20Ashwin%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20experienced%20bowlers%2C%20Pujara%20believes%20the%20team%20may%20need%20Sundar's%20all-round%20abilities%20to%20address%20their%20recent%20batting%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20only%20one%20change%20might%20happen.%20Since%20the%20batting%20wasn't%20good%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%20can%20come%20in%20place%20of%20R%20Ashwin.%20Should%20someone%20come%20in%20place%20of%20Harshit%20Rana%3F%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20no.%20You%20backed%20him%20and%20he%20performed%20well%20in%20the%20first%20match%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pujara%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESundar%2C%20who%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20India's%20memorable%20Brisbane%20victory%20in%202021%2C%20brings%20both%20a%20reliable%20off-spin%20option%20and%20a%20resilient%20lower-order%20batting%20presence.%20With%20Sundar%20in%20the%20mix%2C%20India%20could%20lengthen%20their%20batting%20lineup%20without%20compromising%20their%20bowling%20attack.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20India's%20295-run%20win%20in%20the%20series%20opener%20in%20Perth.%20He%20scalped%20two%20wickets%20and%20contributed%2033%20runs%20in%20the%20match%20before%20making%20way%20for%20Ashwin%20in%20Adelaide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20have%20questioned%20the%20performance%20of%20pacer%20Harshit%20Rana%20after%20he%20conceded%2086%20runs%20in%2016%20overs%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20Pujara%20strongly%20defended%20the%20young%20bowler.%20Rana%2C%20who%20impressed%20with%20a%203%2F48%20spell%20on%20debut%20in%20Perth%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20valuable%20asset%20despite%20his%20recent%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20good%20bowler.%20You%20cannot%20drop%20him%20just%20because%20one%20match%20went%20bad.%20Probably%20the%20only%20change%20for%20me%20would%20be%20Sundar%20for%20Ashwin%20if%20the%20team%20feels%20the%20batting%20lineup%20needs%20strengthening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana's%20pace%20and%20ability%20to%20extract%20bounce%20makes%20him%20a%20compelling%20choice%20for%20the%20Brisbane%20pitch%2C%20known%20for%20its%20lively%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20loss%20in%20Adelaide%20have%20also%20dealt%20a%20blow%20to%20their%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%20qualification%20hopes.%20Currently%20third%20in%20the%20standings%20with%20a%20points%20percentage%20of%2057.29%2C%20India%20face%20an%20uphill%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20secure%20their%20spot%20in%20the%20WTC%20final%2C%20they%20must%20win%20the%20series%20by%20a%20margin%20of%203-1%20or%204-1.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Australia%20sit%20second%20with%20a%2060.71%20points%20percentage%2C%20while%20South%20Africa%20lead%20the%20pack%20with%2063.33.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733834580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fidas4n7_cs_625x300_10_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fbig-change-in-india-xi-for-3rd-australia-test-cheteshwar-pujara-says-batting-wasnt-good-7216239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20a%20crushing%20ten-wicket%20defeat%20to%20Australia%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20India's%20hopes%20of%20bouncing%20back%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20in%20Brisbane%20have%20taken%20centre%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fbig-change-in-india-xi-for-3rd-australia-test-cheteshwar-pujara-says-batting-wasnt-good-7216239%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20May%20Ink%20Deal%20Worth%20Billions%20With%20Russia%20To%20Counter%20China%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20his%20top%20delegation%20of%20defence%20personnel%20continue%20their%20Russia%20visit%2C%20there%20are%20talks%20of%20a%20mega%20defence%20agreement%20between%20Moscow%20and%20New%20Delhi%20being%20in%20advanced%20stages.%20The%20deal%20-%20reportedly%20worth%20%244%20billion%20will%20give%20a%20massive%20boost%20to%20India's%20air%20defence%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20equipment%20being%20discussed%20by%20both%20sides%20is%20the%20advanced%20'Voronezh'%20series%20radar%20which%20is%20manufactured%20by%20Russia's%20Almaz-Antey%20Corporation%2C%20which%20is%20a%20specialist%20organisation%20for%20manufacturing%20anti-aircraft%20missile%20systems%20and%20radars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Voronezh%20radar%20is%20a%20very-long-range%20early%20warning%20radar%20system%20with%20a%20range%20well%20over%208%2C000%20kilometers.%20It%20is%20capable%20of%20identifying%20and%20tracking%20threats%20like%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20fighter%20jets%2C%20and%20ICBMs.%20Should%20India%20acquire%20it%2C%20the%20advanced%20radar%20system%20will%20be%20able%20to%20detect%20any%20air%20threat%20from%20anywhere%20in%20China%2C%20South%20and%20Central%20Asia%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Voronezh%20radar%20can%20detect%20more%20than%20500%20objects%20simultaneously.%20While%20its%20overall%20range%20can%20go%20up%20to%2010%2C000%20kilometers%2C%20it's%20vertical%20range%20exceeds%208%2C000%20km%20and%20horizon%20range%20is%20over%206%2C000%20km.%20Moscow%20claims%20that%20the%20Voronezh%20radar%20system%20can%20even%20track%20stealth%20aircraft.%20Due%20to%20its%20massive%20vertical%20range%2C%20it%20can%20provide%20complete%20data%20about%20ICBMs%20and%20situational%20awareness%20of%20near-Earth%20objects%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3