nities)...%20otherwise%20what%20is%20the%20problem%3F%20Let%20the%20government%20take%20a%20call%20based%20on%20the%20Backward%20Classes%20report%20and%20let%20these%20protests%20continue%20in%20a%20peaceful%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Prashanth%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBroadly%20speaking%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20reneging%20on%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20(when%20the%20latter%20was%20in%20power)%20that%20says%20'status%20quo'%20will%20be%20maintained%20on%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20said%20he%20met%20with%20other%20Lingayat%20Panchamasali%20community%20leaders%20and%20assured%20them%20of%20help%2C%20pending%20submission%20of%20a%20report%20from%20the%20state's%20Backward%20Classes%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Panchamasali%20sect%20of%20the%20Lingayats%20-%20an%20influential%20community%20that%20swung%20heavily%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20won%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20election%20-%20currently%20has%20five%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20state-run%20educational%20institutions%20and%20government%20jobs.%20It%20now%20wants%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733832780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F5gsuueg8_lingayat-panchamasali-protests_625x300_10_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Flingayat-panchamasali-reservation-protests-basavajaya-mrityunjay-swamiji-protests-lathi-charge-in-karnataka-over-lingayat-communitys-quota-demand-7215905%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Protests%20over%20the%20Lingayat%20Panchamasali%20community's%20