0and%20residences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20urbanization%2C%20which%20gave%20people%20more%20access%20to%20resources.%20We%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airport-technology.com%2Fprojects%2Fkempegowda-international-airport-bangalore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarger%20airport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20restaurants%20with%20various%20cuisines%20coming%20into%20the%20city%2C%20and%20affordable%20internet%20access%20due%20to%20more%20competition%20between%20companies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20startup%20ecosystem%2C%20we%20get%20new%20services%20and%20products%20faster%20than%20other%20Indian%20cities.%20I've%20benefited%20positively%20from%20urban%20development%20in%20these%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a15e9ef9-6997-4e3d-8ea0-85d80542c15e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20benefits%20and%20drawbacks%20to%20Bengaluru's%20transformation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20employed%20in%20the%20IT%20sector.%20I've%20been%20working%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-product-manager-got-overseas-transfer-india-us-oracle-swe-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOracle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20past%2027%20years%2C%20and%20my%20current%20role%20is%20solutions%20architect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Bengaluru%20have%20undoubtedly%20benefited%20from%20the%20job%20opportunities%20created%20by%20the%20tech%20boom%2C%20but%20I%20think%20local%20people%20are%20split%20on%20the%20effects%20of%20urbanization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20to%20see%20negative%20comments%20about%20Bengaluru%20on%20social%20media%20or%20people%20complaining%20to%20their%20friends.%20I%20think%20the%20three%20biggest%20issues%20they%20raise%20are%20the%20water%20crisis%2C%20housing%20prices%2C%20and%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Findia%2Fnews%2Fbrace-yourself-bengaluru-traffic-could-get-a-whole-lot-worse-as-bbmp-announces-m