%20two%20have%20been%20held%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20frustration%20of%20candidates.%20The%20Sub-Inspector%20and%20Mahila%20Supervisor%20exams%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20have%20not%20been%20held%20since%202017.%20Under%20the%20Examination%20Act%20of%201937%2C%20recruitment%20exams%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20conducted%20annually%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20for%20several%20key%20exams%2C%20including%20for%20Sub-Engineers%20and%20Forest%20Guards%2C%20have%20also%20been%20pending%20since%202023%2C%20affecting%20two%20lakh%20students%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%2026%20lakh%20registered%20unemployed%20youth%2C%20has%20said%20efforts%20are%20on%20to%20address%20the%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrince%20Gautam%20from%20Satna%20came%20to%20Bhopal%20in%202017%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20Sub-Inspector%20(SI)%20exam.%20After%20failing%20to%20clear%20the%20exam%20that%20year%2C%20he%20stayed%20in%20the%20city%2C%20working%20as%20a%20daily%20wage%20labourer%20to%20support%20his%20studies.%20Today%2C%20Prince%20fears%20becoming%20over-age%2C%20rendering%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20futile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fujlbqs2o_prince-gautam-mp-exam-story_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20here%20to%20study%2C%20but%20poverty%20forced%20me%20into%20labour.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20recruitment%20since%202017%2C%20and%20I%20am%20losing%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Kumar%2C%20another%20candidate%20from%20Umaria%2C%20has%20only%20a%20year%20left%20before%20he%20crosses%20the%20eligibility%20age%20limit%20and%20said%20he%20feels%20abandoned%20by%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F520joo9_ajit-kumar-mp-exam-story_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20is%20a%20small%20farmer.%20I've%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20SI%20exam%20for%20seven%20years.%20If%20this%20continues%2C%20my%20dream%20will%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Pooja%20Kushwaha%20of%20Satna%2C%20the%20struggle%20extends%20beyond%20her%20studies.%20Married%20and%20managing%20household%20responsibilities%2C%20she%20has%20been%20preparing%20for%20the%20Mahila%20Supervisor%20exam%20since%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fh3qm376o_pooja-kushwaha-mp-exam-story_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20last%20year%20before%20becoming%20over-age.%20My%20family%20tells%20me%20to%20quit%20dreaming%20of%20a%20job%20and%20focus%20on%20my%20children.%20But%20how%20can%20I%20give%20up%20after%20so%20much%20effort%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20lamented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinesh%20Chauhan%2C%20from%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Unemployed%20Association%2C%20criticised%20the%20lack%20of%20timely%20exams.%20%26quot%3BAge%20matters%20in%20uniformed%20jobs.%20Every%20year%2C%20lakhs%20of%20youth%20fall%20out%20of%20eligibility%20due%20to%20delays.%20The%20government%20must%20act%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Avnish%20Bundela%20also%20questioned%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20employment.%20%26quot%3BUnemployment%20is%20rising%2C%20and%20the%20government%20must%20explain%20why%20recruitment%20exams%20are%20not%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernm