20is%20no%20longer%20a%20taboo%20subject%20in%20India%20but%20instead%20a%20fundamental%20part%20of%20curriculums%20in%20all%20schools%2C%20both%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%E2%80%99s%20keenness%20in%20the%20subject%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20his%20childhood.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20in%20Class%207%2C%20a%20classmate%20of%20mine%20got%20her%20period.%20The%20boys%20did%20not%20know%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20bleeding%20and%20began%20making%20fun%20of%20her%2C%20assuming%20that%20sex%20had%20caused%20her%20to%20bleed.%E2%80%9D%20That%20day%2C%20a%2012-year-old%20Sandy%20made%20his%20way%20back%20home%20with%20a%20question%20for%20his%20mother.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20and%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3Enot%20speak%20about%20periods%3F%20Is%20it%20something%20secret%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stereotype%20etched%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284174%2Fmenstruation-periods-girls-school-dropout-whisper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscourse%20around%20menstruation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebecame%20evident%20to%20him.%20So%2C%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20to%20see%20the%20ripples%20of%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20being%20catapulted%20across%20200%20slum%20areas%20in%20over%2026%20cities%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20changemaker%20is%20born%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Sandy%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Khanda.%20His%20childhood%20was%20spent%20helping%20his%20father%20take%20care%20of%20the%20paddy.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20would%20often%20hear%20of%20female%20foeticide%2C%20patriarchy%20and%20taboo%20around%20menstrual%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAscribing%20his%20entrepreneurial%20relevance%20to%20his%20roots%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20these%20issues%20but%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20or%20resources%20back%20then.%20I%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20family%20where%20I%20was%20taught%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20make%20a%20career.%20But%20the%20accident%20changed%20everything.%20I%20saw%20this%20as%20the%20second%20chance%20that%20I%20was%20given%20to%20serve%20my%20community%3B%20a%20chance%20to%20utilise%20my%20life%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Periods%20of%20Pride%20focuses%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190014%2Fiit-girl-innovation-low-cost-zero-electricity-device-clean-sanitary-pads-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Slum%20to%20School%E2%80%99%20initiative%20is%20present%20in%2026%20slums%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20enrolling%2062%20children%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Green%20Pencil%20Foundation%20has%20gynaecologists%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20workshops%20that%20are%20conducted%20to%20educate%20women%20about%20reproductive%20and%20menstrual%20health%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-5_11zon-1732888689-768x402.jpg%20768w%2