0information%20can%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20a%20unique%2012-digit%20code%20allowing%20students%20to%20digitally%20store%2C%20manage%2C%20and%20access%20a%20comprehensive%20range%20of%20academic%20information.%20This%20includes%20scorecards%2C%20marksheets%2C%20grade%20sheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20diplomas%2C%20certificates%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20ensures%20smoother%20transitions%20between%20different%20educational%20stages%20and%20institutions%2C%20offering%20significant%20benefits%20for%20students%20pursuing%20education%20across%20various%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20access%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20or%20is%20there%20a%20specific%20process%20to%20follow%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPAAR%20integrates%20with%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC)%2C%20enabling%20students%20to%20accumulate%2C%20transfer%2C%20and%20redeem%20credits%20across%20institutions.%20This%20system%20not%20only%20facilitates%20credit%20transfers%20but%20also%20tracks%20academic%20achievements%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20their%20educational%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20students%20can%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20as%20it%20consolidates%20all%20their%20achievements%20onto%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20creating%20a%20comprehensive%20digital%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20requirements%20for%20applying%20for%20an%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20generating%20an%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20important%20prerequisites%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20UDISE%2B%20(Unified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%20Plus)%20records%20must%20match%20exactly%20with%20the%20name%20as%20per%20their%20Aadhaar.%20This%20ensures%20consistency%20and%20accuracy%20in%20the%20identification%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20Personal%20Education%20Number%20(PEN)%20is%20mandatory%20for%20generating%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20It%20is%20a%20unique%20identification%20number%20for%20students%20across%20all%20the%20education%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20APAAR%20ID%20only%20useful%20for%20current%20students%2C%20or%20can%20it%20benefit%20graduates%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20beneficial%20not%20only%20for%20current%20students%20but%20also%20for%20graduates.%20For%20students%20like%20Krystelle%20Dsouza%2C%20a%20journalist%20pursuing%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20journalism%20at%20Mumbai%20University%2C%20this%20ID%20serves%20as%20a%20long-term%20academic%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20create%20my%20APAAR%20ID%20recently%2C%20and%20it%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC).%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20great%20step%20for%20students%20to%20have%20access%20to%20all%20of%20their%20degree%20certificates%20and%20anything%20they%E2%80%99ve%20accumulated%20throughout%20their%20academic%20trajectory%20in%20one%20place.%E2%80%9D%20This%20highlights%20how%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20helps%20graduates%20manage%20and%20access%20their%20academic%20records%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20achievements%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20easily%20accessible%2C%20even%20after%20completing%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20I%20need%20to%20register%20for%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20and%20how%20do%20I%20get%20started%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20register%20for%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20To%20register%2C%20visit%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website%20%E2%80%93%20abc.gov.in%20and%20click%20on%20%E2%80%98My%20Account%2C%E2%80%99%20then%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98Student%E2%80%99%20option.%20Next%2C%20click%20%E2%80%98Sign%20up%E2%80%99%20and%20provide%20your%20mobile%20number%2C%20address%2C%20and%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F217362%2Fhow-to-get-cbse-10-12-examination-marksheet-migration-certification-online-digilocker-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20a%20DigiLocker%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20logging%20in%20with%20your%20credentials%2C%20DigiLocker%20will%20prompt%20you%20to%20consent%20to%20share%20your%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20with%20ABC%20for%20KYC%20verification.%20Once%20you%20agree%2C%20enter%20your%20academic%20details%2C%20such%20as%20your%20school%20or%20university%20name%2C%20class%2C%20and%20course.%20After%20submitting%20the%20form%2C%20your%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20will%20be%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20you%20download%20your%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20can%20be%20easily%20downloaded%20by%20logging%20into%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website.%20Once%20logged%20in%2C%20students%20can%20navigate%20to%20the%20dashboard%20and%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98APAAR%20card%20download%E2%80%99%20option.%20The%20card%20will%20then%20appear%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20ready%20to%20be%20downloaded%20or%20printed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20We%20will%20update%20the%20latest%20information%20about%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20when%20more%20details%20are%20revealed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733318268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-mobile-1732080263.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20launched%20in%202023%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20provides%20a%20digital%20identity%20that%20helps%20students%20manage%20and%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20across%20multiple%20institutions.%20This%2012-digit%20ID%20consolidates%20information%20like%20marksheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements%20into%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20simplifying%20academic%20transitions%20and%20tracking%20progress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22ca